  "detailed_description": "<h1>Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><i>(Please note that we are a two person indie team and this is a short (2-3.5 hour) game. With that out of the way...) </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485340/extras/26876b70d6118bcc7c22e583d336cd79.avif?t=1701450046\" width=616 height=174 /></span><br><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shoot yourself out of cannons, and <strong>destroy stuff in VR</strong>! Take down structures in creative and explosive ways.<br><br></li><li><strong>Over 50 levels, and secret areas</strong>, present new challenges and puzzles, allowing you to strategize and plan your destructive path. <br><br></li><li><strong>Splinter wood, and  shatter rock</strong>... or whatever gets in your way! Create <strong>magnificent chaos</strong> by experimenting with different angles, velocities, and <strong>explosives</strong> to obliterate everything in your way!<br><br></li><li>Perfect your skills and <strong>earn the high score</strong> by using the fewest shots possible to cause the most destruction! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485340/extras/7431852f4189ca6622dd3e53da7666ef.avif?t=1701450046\" width=616 height=174 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><br>You're one of a few surviving woodland Otters, fighting to take back your home from an invading army of adorable but absolutely <i>evil</i> Beavers. It's time for revenge!<br><br>Get ready to embark on an adrenaline-pumping, physics shaking adventure like no other with Cannon Fotter, the <strong>ultimate VR tower destruction game</strong>! Made by a two person team, Cannon Fotter makes you the master of demolition, armed with nothing but your courage, a powerful cannon, and your body.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485340/extras/0ee610aaf983dbb6a8f112891da43181.poster.avif?t=1701450046\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485340/extras/0ee610aaf983dbb6a8f112891da43181.webm?t=1701450046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485340/extras/0ee610aaf983dbb6a8f112891da43181.mp4?t=1701450046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>(Please note that we are a two person indie team and this is a short (2-3.5 hour) game. With that out of the way...) </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485340/extras/26876b70d6118bcc7c22e583d336cd79.avif?t=1701450046\" width=616 height=174 /></span><br><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shoot yourself out of cannons, and <strong>destroy stuff in VR</strong>! Take down structures in creative and explosive ways.<br><br></li><li><strong>Over 50 levels, and secret areas</strong>, present new challenges and puzzles, allowing you to strategize and plan your destructive path. <br><br></li><li><strong>Splinter wood, and  shatter rock</strong>... or whatever gets in your way! Create <strong>magnificent chaos</strong> by experimenting with different angles, velocities, and <strong>explosives</strong> to obliterate everything in your way!<br><br></li><li>Perfect your skills and <strong>earn the high score</strong> by using the fewest shots possible to cause the most destruction! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485340/extras/7431852f4189ca6622dd3e53da7666ef.avif?t=1701450046\" width=616 height=174 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><br>You're one of a few surviving woodland Otters, fighting to take back your home from an invading army of adorable but absolutely <i>evil</i> Beavers. It's time for revenge!<br><br>Get ready to embark on an adrenaline-pumping, physics shaking adventure like no other with Cannon Fotter, the <strong>ultimate VR tower destruction game</strong>! Made by a two person team, Cannon Fotter makes you the master of demolition, armed with nothing but your courage, a powerful cannon, and your body.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485340/extras/0ee610aaf983dbb6a8f112891da43181.poster.avif?t=1701450046\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485340/extras/0ee610aaf983dbb6a8f112891da43181.webm?t=1701450046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485340/extras/0ee610aaf983dbb6a8f112891da43181.mp4?t=1701450046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
